title: Pho Hao Bistro
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Thai, Delivery, Take-out, Asian, Vietnamese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a separate vegan and vegetarian menu. Vegan items include rice dishes, noodle dishes, soup dishes, vegan eggrolls and mango spring rolls among others. Vegan drinks include hot tea, iced teas, organic rice milk tea drinks, coconut thai iced teas, taro teas, smoothies, lemonades, fruit mixed drinks. Does not use MSG.
